ad the label carefully before use | Do not exceed the recommended dose | Keep out of the reach of children | Store in a cool dry place away from direct sunlight and heat','','Bilva Leaf','','1/a/3, plot, 9-63, no 20, road no. 3, brindavan colony, boduppal, hyderabad, telangana 500092','SOLD OUT','India'),(321,'Shri Nath Daiocare with Aloe Vera Gel 10gm free','Ayurveda','Diabetes Care','Shri Nath Pharmacy','200 gm Powder','jar of 200 gm Powder',175,175,'','NO','','Shri Nath Daiocare helps to stimulate the pancreatic cells to produce more insulin thereby controlling the blood sugar levels. It is rich in antioxidants and thus maintains the body\'s oxidative balance. | Key Ingredients: Chiraita Indrayan Neem leaves Neemboli Sanay leaves Jamun Guthili Triphala | Key Benefits: It aids treatment of diabetes It is used to repair damaged cells It promotes the process of healing It helps in providing the body with needed nourishment Expiry date: 36 months from date of mfg | Directions For Use: Consume 2 to 4 gm twice a day with water or as directed by the physician. | Safety Information: Read the label carefully before use Store in a cool dry place away from direct sunlight Keep out of reach of the children','','','Shri Nath Daiocare with Aloe Vera Gel 10gm free Shri Nath Daiocare helps to stimulate the pancreatic cells to produce more insulin thereby controlling the blood sugar levels. It is rich in antioxidants and thus maintains the body\'s oxidative balance.','','It aids treatment of diabetes | It is used to repair damaged cells | It promotes the process of healing | It helps in providing the body with needed nourishment |','','Consume 2 to 4 gm twice a day with water or as directed by the physician.','','Read the label carefully before use | Store in a cool dry place away from direct sunlight | Keep out of reach of the children','','Chiraita | Indrayan | Neem leave | Neemboli | Sanay leave | Jamun Guthili | Triphala','','Paradigm Healthcare Services, # 1454, Housing Boar