 you have deep skin | Keep it for 15 minutes for whitish skin and a bit longer if you have fair skin | Bleach should be used once in every 2-3weeks | Or use as directed by the physician','','Patch test is recommended for first time users | Do not use soap for 5 hours after the bleach | Read the label carefully before use | Keep out of the reach of children | Avoid going into sunlight immediately','','Hydrogen Peroxide | Polyquaternium Compound | Powder Activator Perulphate | Pre Bleach Cream Glycerin, Silicon Blend, Allantoin, Acetyl Tetrapeptide','','VLCC Health Care Limited , M-14, Greater Kailash II Commercial Complex, New Delhi – 110048, India','SOLD OUT','India'),(327,'Zinnia Wellness Irani Fenugreek Extract Veggie Capsule','Ayurveda','Diabetes Care','Zinnia Wellness','60 vegicaps','bottle of 60 vegicaps',899,899,'','NO','','Zinnia Wellness Irani Fenugreek Extract Veggie Capsule contains fenugreek which has some amazing health benefits that could transform health. Besides helping with various digestive problems such as upset stomach, constipation and stomach inflammation, it is also used for the treatment of diabetes, obesity, painful menstruation and PCOS. | Key Ingredients: Fenugreek seed extract (40% saponin)- 500 mg | Key Benefits: Helps to balance blood sugar levels Treats upset stomach, constipation and stomach inflammation Used in the treatment of diabetes, obesity, painful menstruation and PCOS | Directions For Use: Take 1 capsule daily or as directed by a healthcare professional. | Safety Information: Read the label carefully before use Keep out of reach of the children Store in a cool dry place','','','Zinnia Wellness Irani Fenugreek Extract Veggie Capsule Zinnia Wellness Irani Fenugreek Extract Veggie Capsule contains fenugreek which has some amazing health benefits that could transform health. Besides helping with various digestive problems such as upset stomach, constipation and stomach inflammation, it is also used for the treatment of diabetes, obesity, painful menstruation and PCOS.','','Helps to balance blood sugar levels | Treats upset stomach, constipation and stomach inflammation | Used in the treatment of diabetes, obesity, painful menstruation and PCOS','','Take 1 capsule daily or as directed by a healthcare professional.','','Read the label carefully before use | Keep out of reach of the children | Store in a cool dry place','','Fenugreek eed extract (40% aponin)- 500 mg','','97, Shyam - 3, Industrial Estate, Changodar, Ahmedabad - 382213, Gujarat, India','SOLD OUT','India'),(328,'Khadi Naturals Ayurvedic Neem Face Wash','Ayurveda','Ayurveda Personal Care','Khadi Naturals','210 ml Face Wash','bottle of 210 ml Face Wash',165,175,'','NO','','Khadi Naturals Ayurvedic Neem Face Wash Neem face wash contains natural neem leaf extracts which are generally known for their therapeutic properties. It helps to remove signs of dirt and oiliness. It helps to maintain skin free from toxins and keep away the development of any kind of skin inflammation. | Key Ingredients: Neem | Key Benefits: It improves general skin health and immunity, combating bacterial infections such as acne and boils Neem tackles bacteria from the root thus preventing the recurrence of pimples and blemishes It helps to even out the skin tone and colour It also helps to retain the skin\'s elasticity, making it supple | Directions For Use: Use as directed on the label or as advised by your healthcare provider | Safety Information: Read the label carefully before use Store in a cool and dry place away from direct sunlight Keep out of reach of children','','','Khadi Naturals Ayurvedic Neem Face Wash Khadi Naturals Ayurvedic Neem Face Wash Neem face wash contains natural neem leaf extracts which are generally known for their therapeutic properties. It helps to remove signs of dirt and oiliness. It helps to maintain skin free from toxins and keep away the development of any kind of skin inflammation.','','It improves general skin health and immunity, combating bacterial infections such as acne and boils | Neem tackles bacteria from the root thus preventing the recurrence of pimples and blemishes | It helps to even out the skin tone and colour | It also helps to retain the skin\'s elasticity, making it supple','','Use as directed on the label or as advised by your healthcare provider','','Read the label carefully before use | Store in a cool and dry place away from direct sunlight | Keep out of reach of children','','Neem','','703-705, Shahpuri Tower, Community Center, C-58, Janakpuri, New Delhi, Delhi 110058','SOLD OUT','India'),(329,'Vaidyaratnam Oushadha Soap','Ayurveda','Ayurveda Personal Care','Ashtavaidyan Thaikkattu Mooss Vaidyaratnam Pvt Ltd','75 gm Soap','box of 75 gm Soap',35,0,'','NO','','Vaidyaratnam Oushadha Soap is a natural transparent soap, suitable for all skin type. | Key Ingredients: Sodium Cocoate Sodium Stearate Tera Sodium EDTA Castor Oil Glycerin Herbal Extract Moisturizer BHT Perfume | Key Benefits: It gently cleanses the skin and keeps your skin moisturized all the time Prevents skin problems such as dryness, scaling etc. It prevents the skin from developing wrinkles Promotes glowing and healthy looking skin | Directions For Use: Use daily during bathing | Safety Information: Read the label carefully before use Keep out of the reach of children Store in a cool and dry place, away from sunlight For external use only','','','Vaidyaratnam Oushadha Soap Vaidyaratnam Oushadha Soap is a natural transparent soap, suitable for all skin type.','','It gently cleanses the skin and keeps your skin moisturized all the time | Prevents skin problems such as dryness, scaling etc. | It prevents the skin from developing wrinkles | Promotes glowing and healthy looking skin','','Use daily during bathing','','Read the label carefully before use | Keep out of the reach of children | Store in a cool and dry place, away from sunlight | For external use only','','Sodium Cocoate | Sodium Stearate | Tera Sodiu